        {
            "title": "沃爾核材今通過上市聆訊 現市值約400億元人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港交所(00388)資料顯示，早於2007年已在深圳上市的沃爾核材(002130.SZ)，今日剛通過來港上市聆訊。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">該公司A股今早跌1.95%，中午收報32.69元(人民幣‧下同)，市值達411.86億元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15615461-%e6%b2%83%e7%88%be%e6%a0%b8%e6%9d%90%e4%bb%8a%e9%80%9a%e9%81%8e%e4%b8%8a%e5%b8%82%e8%81%86%e8%a8%8a-%e7%8f%be%e5%b8%82%e5%80%bc%e7%b4%84400%e5%84%84%e5%85%83%e4%ba%ba%e5%b9%a3",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2026/01/002130-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-27 12:42:41",
